flowPara.flowSpan: Make sure to follow the setup guide before installing.
See the command line tutorial for more information on managing Flatpak applications from the command line.

flowRoot.flowPara: These wireframes are primarily schematic. Key features:
- Short, prominent description of what flathub is
- Clear entry point for users wanting to install apps
- Prominent placement of the setup guide - needed to ensure that users can install apps
- Installation options for both app centers and command line
